test_plan.display_value:
1. Impersonate some of the users whose Employee Status contains 'pme' (for example, Denae Vaughn)
2. Go to TCP and add an empty time card (with 0 time recorded for every day)
3. Submit it
4. Impersonate the approver of the time sheet (if it's Denae Vaughn, the approver is Brittany Jackson) and approve this time card
5. For other users, it should not be possible to do it
